  ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Tools > Board          : ATtiny13
  Tools > BOD            : [Use any BOD level you like]
  Tools > Clock          : 9.6 MHz or 4.8 MHz depending on what osc. to tune
  Tools > Timing         : Millis disabled, Micros disabled

